quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Ruri! Re ile Ra romella Nooe ho batho ba habo: “Lemosa batho ba heno esere kahlolo e mahlonoko ea tloha ea ba oela holimo"
  71,2,"A re: “Oho batho ba heso! Ruri! Ke mohlokomelisi ea totobetseng ho lona"
  71,3,"“Hore le tlameha ho khumamela Allah le hona ho mo sebeletsa ka tieo, le nkutloe"
  71,4,"“Hore A tle A le ts’oarele libe tsa lona le hona ho lelefatsa nako ea lona ea pallo. Hobane Ruri! Nako eo pallo ea Allah e tlang, e ke ke ea liehisoa hoja le ne le tseba.”"
  71,5,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! Ke ne ke etsa pitso ho batho ba heso bosiu le mots’eare"
  71,6,Empa lipitso tsohle tsa ka ha li’a ka tsa thusa letho haese hona hore ba balehe ‘neteng
  71,7,"“Hobane ka linako tsohle ha ke ba bitsetsa hore U tle U ba ts’oarele, ba kiba litsebe tsa bona ka menoana le hona ho ipata lifahleho ka liaparo tsa bona; ba tsitlaletse nyefolong le hona ho ikhohomosa"
  71,8,“Ke ba hoelelitse ka lentsoe le phahameng
  71,9,“Ke ile ka phatlalatsa molaetsa pooaneng ho bona; ka etsa kopo ho bona sephiring
  71,10,"“Ke re: kopang ts’oarelo ho Mong`a lona. Hobane U Ts’oarela ka Mehla eohle"
  71,11,“Etsoe U tla le nesetsa lipula tsa litloebelele
  71,12,“A le ekeletse maruo le bara; A le sitse ka Lirapa le Linoka tse phallang
  71,13,“Molato ke eng ka lona haele moo le hloka ts’epo ho Allah molemong oa boits’oaro bo nepahetseng
  71,14,Empa e le Eena Ea le hlotseng ka mekhahlelo e fapaneng
  71,15,Na ha le bone kamoo Allah a hlotseng maholimo a supileng kateng ka tatellano
  71,16,A tsepamisa ngoeli ho ba khanya leholimong le lona letsatsi ho ba lebone
  71,17,“Ke Allah ea le hlahisitseng leroleng la lefats’e
  71,18,"“Pheletsong U tla boela A le busetsa ho lona hape, U tla le tsosa hape ka Letsatsi la Tsoho"
  71,19,“Allah U le aletse lefats’e
  71,20,“Hore le tle le hahlaule holim’a lona ka litsela tse pharaletseng.”
  71,21,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! ba ntatotse, eaba ba sala morao batho bao thepa le bana ba bona li sa tl’ong ho ba thusa ka letho haese Tahleho"
  71,22,“Ba lohile leqheka le ts’abehang
  71,23,"“Ba re: “Le se lahle melingoana ea lona kherehloa. E leng Wadd kapa Suw’a, le haele Yaghuth, Ya’uq kapa Nasr"
  71,24,"Ruri! Ba khelositse batho ba bangata tseleng, uena ha ho kamoo u ka putsang baetsalibe kateng haese ka ho kheloha.”"
  71,25,"Ba ile ba khamisoa metsi ho latela libe tsa bona, eaba ba akheloa Mollong. Ha ho bathusi ba ileng ba ba fumana ntle ho Allah"
  71,26,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! U se siee leha e le moneketsela feela oa moetsalibe lefats’eng"
  71,27,"Hobane haeba U ka ba siea, ba tla khelosa makhabunyane a Hau le tsoala tsa bona e tla ba baetsalibe"
  71,28,"Mong`a ka! U nts’oarele ‘moho le batsoali ba ka le ba-kholoang bohle ba keneng lelapeng la ka, banna le basali, U se ke oa putsa baetsalibe ka letho haese timelo"